        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " But some will possibly say: How doth this follow? Suppose it true, that Christ be risen, how doth it follow, that the dead shall rise? The force of it lieth in several things: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
